      • update

        public void update(org.apache.felix.service.command.CommandSession session,
                   String userPass,
                   String idmUrl,
                   String idmPort,
                   boolean acceptLicense,
                   boolean skipRepoUpdatePreview,
                   long maxJobsFinishWaitTimeMs,
                   long maxUpdateWaitTimeMs,
                   String logFilePath,
                   boolean quietMode,
                   String archive)
            throws org.forgerock.json.resource.ResourceException
        Handles the Update (upgrade/patch) process.
        Parameters:
        session - session that invoked the command.
        userPass - user:passwd to be used on rest calls.
        idmUrl - url to the idm instance.
        idmPort - port that idm is running on.
        acceptLicense - if true, the accept license step is skipped.
        archive - The simple file name of the archive that is already in bin/update.
        Throws:
        org.forgerock.json.resource.ResourceException
